GDG Algiers is a local community

situated at the Higher National

School of Computer Science in

Algiers (ESI ex INI), Algiers, Algeria.
 
It is part of the big global communi

-ty of developers "Google Develop

-ers Group" an inclusive 

environment where everyone and

anyone interested in tech is

welcome to join.

Our community gathers motivated
 
young students with similar

interests in Google technologies

and devoted developers.
